	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am currently camping this floating turd for a pendant...as a 45 monk all the nearly all the clockworks in the joint are green with the exception of a few XA XB and XC models....i am dubious now to them and despite what i have heard from other sources, none of the gnomes or clockworks aggro when another is attacked or if the lava elemental is attacked....this might change if my faction worsens.  Ive spent about 20 hours in that room and have seen 0 pendants....i think i am quite unlucky but it is very bad....<br>fighting the elemental isnt too hard unless he has his nasty damage shield up...in which case i, having no way to dispell him, just FDed healed up timed how long it takes for him to recast the damage shield, its 5 minutes so just hang out wait and attack when the 5 minutes is up. there are 5 spawn points in the room 4 of which are stationary near the 4 pillars in the room. the 5th spawn is a wanderer just walks around the room....this is either the lava elemental or the PH.....the spawn time for the room is 20 minutes...good luck, or at least better luck than ive had<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
